Melt margarine in large saucepan over low heat. Add marshmallows and stir until completely melted. Remove from heat. Stir in vanilla. Stir in KELLOGG'S* RICE KRISPIES* cereal until well coated. Using lightly buttered spatula, press into buttered 3.5 L (13x9-inch) pan. Allow mixture to cool. Cut into bars. Best if served same day.